NOTE: 
Five of the 14 six-digit NAICS industries with products affected by Chinese retaliatory tariffs do not have employment data publicly available. To ensure full coverage of all products affected by the tariffs, the author team used five-digit NAICS industries, which are more expansive, in instances where six-digit industry data were unavailable. Column D includes county-level employment in 5-digit industries affected by Chinese tariffs, while Column E contains county-level employment in 6-digit industries affected by Chinese tariffs.
